reviewText: This is our favorite Elmo DVD. The robot storyline is very cute, and the Elmo segments from various Sesame Street episodes are well-chosen. I love "New Way to Walk," though I remember it with the Oinker Sisters when I was a kid. Destiny's Child does a good job with it.
